    "description": "超心智是一款基于组合的第一人称解谜游戏。我们设计了四种能力：施加速度，锁，放大和反重力，这使得玩家能充分利用想象力去发掘解决谜题的可能性。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >速度</h2>通过给目标加速来远程移动方块或是按下控制器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/1bdf3532c9cf12dd0cc59abae6e11cd8.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/1bdf3532c9cf12dd0cc59abae6e11cd8.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/1bdf3532c9cf12dd0cc59abae6e11cd8.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >锁</h2>将方块固定在某个位置或是保持控制器按下/松开。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/c8b532e0de965eb7106f58f2a57890f2.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/c8b532e0de965eb7106f58f2a57890f2.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/c8b532e0de965eb7106f58f2a57890f2.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放大</h2>将方块的体积和质量翻倍。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/5ef7ff022625c2a35657d5363e9195a5.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/5ef7ff022625c2a35657d5363e9195a5.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/5ef7ff022625c2a35657d5363e9195a5.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >反重力</h2>反转方块的重力方向。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/ac9ea76abe30403fcdb8662229b2c9f3.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/ac9ea76abe30403fcdb8662229b2c9f3.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/ac9ea76abe30403fcdb8662229b2c9f3.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >锁进阶</h2>锁住方块的状态。玩家就能对额外一个目标使用放大/反重力能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/24bba518ae0052833b9c09cacea5ada6.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/24bba518ae0052833b9c09cacea5ada6.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/24bba518ae0052833b9c09cacea5ada6.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >能力的组合</h2>所有的能力可以以任意方式组合，因此玩家可以通过多种方式解决谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/3b6220932fccc200655d3f052169e981.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/3b6220932fccc200655d3f052169e981.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/3b6220932fccc200655d3f052169e981.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >作用自身</h2>大部分能力可以作用到自身。你的角色能被击飞，锁住或是放大。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/cb8cf04017846cc3698104905e8ff9ea.poster.avif?t=1647669901\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/cb8cf04017846cc3698104905e8ff9ea.webm?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889330/extras/cb8cf04017846cc3698104905e8ff9ea.mp4?t=1647669901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>QQ群：364695780<br>微博：@递归工作室",
